stimulus:
Ready-Set-Go Task:

  • Blue circle ("Ready") appears
  • Then, after a delay, a green circle ("Set") appears
  • After "Set" disappears, screen goes blank
  • You must press SPACE or tap the screen when you think the same delay has passed
  • After you press, a red circle will appear
  • Then you'll see how close your timing was (only for the first 5 trials).
